FAME CELEBRITY GPS! *EXCLUSIVE* - @markwahlberg and @kevinhart4real run back and forth to their car wearing tracksuits, as they film an action scene with a large tortoise for their upcoming film 'Me Time' in Los Angeles. Mark Wahlberg and Kevin Hart run back and forth to their car wearing tracksuits, as they film an action scene in which they carry a very large tortoise to an emergency room for their upcoming film 'Me Time' in Los Angeles on Friday.
Today TMZ has reported that paramedics were on the scene at Sunset Gower Studios attending to a crew member on the set of “ Me Time’' According to the report, a 38-year-old male fell from a catwalk this morning 30 feet in the air sustaining fractures to his legs and arms. The male did not appear to be wearing a safety harness. According to the report, the fall was so bad, paramedics had to use a defibrillator to get a heartbeat back. His condition remains unknown. *Shot on September 10, 2021* #fame #famebysheeraz #sheerazhasan #sheerazinc #sheeraz
